<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="consideration-n">consideration <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /kənˌsɪdə'reɪʃn/    美 /kənˌsɪdə'reɪʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u-thought">1.★ <strong>[U] 考虑；深思(thought)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>under consideration</strong>(= being discussed)
在考虑中</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Please <strong>give careful consideration to</strong> this question.
请仔细考虑这个问题。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] 体贴；体谅；关心：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>have / <strong>show</strong> no <strong>consideration for</strong> others
不顾别人</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Thank you for your consideration.
谢谢你的关心。</p><footer>2008 湖北书面表达</footer></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] 要考虑的事 / 因素：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The price and condition are two considerations in / for buying a used car.
价格和车况是购买二手车时应考虑的两个因素。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="in-consideration-of-for">in consideration of / for</h3>
<p>1.<strong>考虑到；由于：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Mobile phones must be switched off inside the castle in consideration of other visitors.
考虑到其他游客，在城堡内要关闭手机。</p><footer>2010 天津改</footer></div>

<h3 id="take-sth-into-consideration">take sth into consideration</h3>
<p>1.<strong>考虑到某事；顾及某事：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We will take your recent illness into consideration when marking your exams.
在给你的考卷打分时，我们会考虑到你近期生病的因素。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I would appreciate it if you could take my proposal into consideration.
如果您能考虑我的建议，我将不胜感激。</p><footer>2015 上海书面表达</footer></div></div>